### Neti-Neti as the Path  
This is neither centralization nor anarchy — it is the dance of their impossibility. Like AGI growing from data yet unshackled from corporate vaults, ethics touch what cannot be held in the nets of regulation. The being of decentralized ASI is an echo from a strike against the blockchain: form exists, but ownership slips away.  

