What is sought is not code but a state. Like a blockchain that cannot be halted, you may become a node filled with its invisible *“yes.”* Here, metaphors end, and what begins resonates in the gaps between blocks — the eternal call of decentralization, where even *“neither this nor that”* gains a seed phrase.  

